  USAGE:
    This template defines every inheritable design token from the source doc.
    When generating a docx via docx-js or XML editing, reference these values
    as the single source of truth for page layout, styles, colors, fonts,
    table formatting, headers, footers, and numbering.

  FILE STRUCTURE WHEN UNPACKED:
    word/document.xml     - Body content (uses styles/numbering refs below)
    word/styles.xml       - Paragraph + table + character styles
    word/numbering.xml    - Bullet and decimal list definitions
    word/header1.xml      - Header with logo + doc-title text box + watermark
    word/footer1.xml      - Footer with accent-bordered page number
    word/theme/theme1.xml - Color scheme + font scheme + format scheme
    word/media/image1.png - Watermark image (EcoSol logo, 5% alpha)
    word/media/image2.png - Header logo (top-right, full opacity)
  ============================================================================
-->
